description: There was a massive response to Kenzie Madison having his feet tickled, so that's exactly what we've got for you here. Tied down tight with his feet roped together, Sebastian begins to torment helpless Kenzie. Incredibly ticklish, even the lightest touch, it drives Kenzie wild as he begs and pleads for Sebastian to stop! Having none of it, Sebastian finds all his most sensitive spots and begins tormenting each one without a care for Kenzie's continued protests.
title: Kenzie Madison & Sebastian Kane
